WEBVTT

00:03:29.627 --> 00:03:32.147
he publicly came out as gay,
and was instrumental

00:03:32.147 --> 00:03:36.660
in drawing attention to the AIDS crisis
until his death in 1987.

00:03:36.660 --> 00:03:37.923
In 2013,

00:03:37.923 --> 00:03:40.470
fifty years after the March On Washington,

00:03:40.470 --> 00:03:43.519
President Barack Obama posthumously 
awarded him

00:03:43.519 --> 00:03:45.539
the Presidential Medal of Freedom,

00:03:45.539 --> 00:03:48.560
praising Rustin’s 
“march towards true equality,

00:03:48.560 --> 00:03:53.400
no matter who we are 
or who we love.”